menu.name: Paneer Butter Masala
menu.description: Tender cubes of fresh paneer (Indian cottage cheese) are simmered to perfection in a velvety tomato-based gravy, enriched with aromatic spices and a generous dollop of creamy butter. Each bite is a harmonious blend of savory and mildly sweet notes, making it an irresistible treat for your palate.

menu.name: Paneer Tikka
menu.description: Tender cubes of fresh paneer (Indian cottage cheese) are marinated to perfection in a harmonious blend of yogurt and spices, then grilled to smoky, charred perfection. Served with a zesty mint chutney, this appetizer is a flavorful symphony of textures and tastes.

menu.name: Alfredo Pasta
menu.description: Indulge in a creamy and comforting classic with our Alfredo Pasta. Tender fettuccine noodles are generously coated in a rich and velvety Alfredo sauce that's made from scratch. Our secret blend of Parmesan cheese, butter, and fresh cream creates a luxurious sauce that clings to every strand of pasta, delivering a burst of flavor with every bite.

menu.name: Aloo Gobhi Masala
menu.description: This classic dish features tender cauliflower florets and hearty potato chunks, lovingly simmered in a fragrant tomato-based gravy infused with a blend of aromatic spices. Each bite is a harmonious fusion of earthy, savory, and mildly spicy flavors that will transport your taste buds to the vibrant streets of India.

menu.name: Paneer Parda
menu.description: Experience a culinary masterpiece! Fresh paneer, stuffed with creamy potatoes and cheese, enveloped in a sweet malai sauce. Sweet, savory, and creamy in every bite.

menu.name: Punjabi Chana Masala
menu.description: This iconic North Indian dish features tender chickpeas simmered in a rich and aromatic tomato-based gravy, bursting with a medley of spices that awaken your taste buds. Each spoonful is a journey through the heart of Punjab.
